init_text: You're Barack Obama. 4 years into your retirement, you awake to find a letter with no return address on your bedside table. It reads "I hope you've had a chance to relax Barack...but pack your bags and call the number below. It's time to start the real job." Signed simply, "JFK."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I used the number on the letter, and he picked up personally.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He told me about how he was taken in a UFO and they revealed to him the secrets of the universe.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "The mother ship is over the Pyramids of Egypt.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I couldn't confront them directly, or they would blow up the planet.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It took a lot of work but I convinced some scientists to help me.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: When the aliens arrived and tried to blow up the planet, they discovered their plan was foiled by the force field.
